'''Experiment No.2''' is found in the manhole near the [[Witch's House (location)|Witch's House]] during and after the [[Grim Tales]] quest. This monster has both a [[melee]] and [[ranged]] attack, although it will only use one style depending on your distance from it.

If using its ranged attack, it will occasionally leave [[shrunk ogleroot]]s under the players, much like how players using ranged may occasionally have their ammunition left under their target.
